reviewText: Awesome match. Sexy Karen Konyha goes toe- to-toe with the equally beautiful Heather Heist. This is my favorite match from premier productions. It starts out with the ladies individually stretching in the pre-match, afterwards the match begins. It's mind-boggling to watch these gorgeous ladies in their sexy bikinis as they wrestle it out in the warm-up phase. You can clearly hear the phrase "let's take these off" as they go topless, and the real match starts. Lots of grapevine pins applied between the two. This was a classic match. I got my money's worth and I loved this bout. Get it now.
